### Insights

| Method | Path | Auth | Roles | Purpose |
|--------|------|------|-------|---------|
| GET | `/api/insights` | Yes | owner, manager | List insights |
| PUT | `/api/insights/[id]` | Yes | owner, manager | Mark as read |

**GET `/api/insights`**
```
Query:    ?businessId=uuid&type=low_stock|reorder|...&unreadOnly=boolean
Response: { data: Insight[] }
```

